null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1726140801497135", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "All On Board! - Demo", "keywords": ["tabletop", "indie", "multiplayer", "online", "board"], "long_description": "All On Board! es una plataforma de juegos de mesa creada desde cero para la realidad virtual, hecha por y para los amantes de los juegos de mesa. Como **la \u00fanica plataforma nativa para VR**, All On Board! aprovecha al m\u00e1ximo las capacidades de la realidad virtual para ofrecer una **experiencia inigualable**. Esto incluye la **selecci\u00f3n predictiva** y el posicionamiento de los elementos del tablero, con **interacciones f\u00edsicas realistas** y cercanas a la vida real. Es **una plataforma que evoluciona constantemente**, tanto en su funcionalidad como en su cat\u00e1logo de juegos, con **franquicias muy queridas** por los fans de los juegos de mesa.\n\nDescubre nuevos juegos como si estuvieras explorando las \u00faltimas novedades de tu tienda favorita. All On Board! te ofrece momentos compartidos de debate, risas y nostalgia, recordando partidas y aventuras inolvidables.\n\n# Caracter\u00edsticas:\n\n- **Solo un jugador necesita comprar el juego**: si lo tienes, invita a tus amigos a jugar gratis, \u00a1igual que en la vida real!\n- **Interacciones intuitivas e inmersivas**.\n- **Los mejores juegos adaptados para VR**, asegurando jugabilidad y fluidez excepcionales.\n- Aprende r\u00e1pido con **tutoriales integrados y ayuda contextual**.\n- **Juegos para 1 o varios jugadores**, con modos en solitario y cooperativo. \u00a1Incluso puedes jugar juegos cooperativos por tu cuenta!\n- **Compatibilidad entre plataformas**.\n- Juega en tu idioma preferido, con **soporte de idiomas en constante expansi\u00f3n**.", "short_description": "Dise\u00f1ado desde cero para la realidad virtual, All On Board! te ofrece experiencias de juegos de mesa sin igual. \u00danete a esta plataforma en constante evoluci\u00f3n y conecta con otros entusiastas de los juegos de mesa. Elige tu avatar y disfruta jugando solo o con amigos, sumergi\u00e9ndote en algunas de las franquicias de juegos de mesa m\u00e1s populares."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Portrait.png", "id": "1704444607063428", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974853_1704444610396761_8129462956027802645_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5XDcyq96-f8Q7kNvgHhEEKJ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDdaNTpWEyBJL7JKxE5ufyuXf6m3gDwhOCb3aq0O0Ce5g&oe=6713A2A1"}, {"file_name": "Mini Landscape.png", "id": "1091753125993492", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001676_1091753129326825_7961234834135647978_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zt4c_bmbZKcQ7kNvgHoZYmm&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBDJKIhGTH-wfRQD4AZ2EJZUxcQMLAZE-CeeednHI__FQ&oe=6713A1E9"}, {"file_name": "AllOnBoard_LogoRGB.png", "id": "1082541793385056", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031606_1082541796718389_309962359528750378_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=z7RbxQMFo_4Q7kNvgHM9DDd&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDlZHRrPqYgtFmMjlpld0PGfdceVz2X9rnqfJvtHGpTFw&oe=67139306"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1043216403795696", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974551_1043216407129029_2533777505259779871_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ilLEA8Xi-swQ7kNvgFISXgx&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDKwwjbM0FVJCropEPri-qynnvaW9KlKi8yutbz2EvVGw&oe=67139767"}, {"file_name": "Square.png", "id": "883361950081679", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75630196_883361956748345_3217241762219801412_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Nn-dH8xJbSgQ7kNvgER4FTr&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBiT3Mebe5ux4QxWXlio6uVMwtLO9ni0yJWkVqoc5J-rg&oe=671382EB"}, {"file_name": "Hero Cover.png", "id": "452543921151009", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974821_452543924484342_1441901165326065131_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0Pju1lpZn04Q7kNvgHo-bZI&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD09NPAmW4uFj2NVYoPcSl92-ai3ti0U4yQnqI_sltPXg&oe=67138549"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "444485655415207", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031639_444485658748540_2004858343361051430_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mVPtELvWLKkQ7kNvgE5_Tbq&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD8iKIdPZ7w2iYOe51yzIrM-deSoOIWC6JqhzTr98iAsQ&oe=6713A7F7"}]}, "id": "1566053697633818", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "MR_2560x1440.png", "id": "3926993714243148", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75540501_3926993717576481_5999768018423374910_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TwhvrZxDDeYQ7kNvgFCGyHT&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCOLkOSGSuvuaCh1hid2q7oXqH7nUeXTrUZpgUPh6YlyQ&oe=67139197"}, {"file_name": "Istanbul_2560x1440.png", "id": "1609506353108476", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035469_1609506356441809_5222853278055771583_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=MM09ZH4WgVwQ7kNvgHuPoAW&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBIF59ytNHTPfgo9mjrSiMwlVHRmCoMWgt8f-iGeaBMUA&oe=67138601"}, {"file_name": "ETDC_2560x1440.png", "id": "457727553971002", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974527_457727557304335_3237724291120605108_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rEMlsv0YWB8Q7kNvgG3E9N7&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDleTd3gbII9L-nJ9KE5Wn6mmgdlBG9yL3xXfbU0Fqd_A&oe=6713A6E8"}, {"file_name": "RallymanGT_2560x1440.png", "id": "461759443544695", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031359_461759446878028_1513041090128553992_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qtl7p6JeBLIQ7kNvgFWqyyV&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAkuXlpUPiSZ1FFPjUgL9UHUGr84XBNo7guht4RZMblMw&oe=671399B9"}, {"file_name": "TBI_2560x1440.png", "id": "3832428817085206", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57572940_3832428820418539_7817805165391346146_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=vmLYK1APZrcQ7kNvgEPExmz&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC-Ortk0vNY21GDWgYFTreqv7A3CZSfWXgW3gMMzkI7lA&oe=67137FC5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover Image.png", "id": "552619510764476", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570288_552619514097809_150010993699126353_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YWdsXOMo6ygQ7kNvgEcTWMw&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCok10frIkzReGLBBSirvbMTAa0UZfEWyzKWTYJPl8H-w&oe=6713B19C"}, "display_name": "All On Board! - Demo", "keywords": ["tabletop", "board", "multiplayer", "dice", "card"], "long_description": "All On Board! is a revolutionary tabletop platform built from the ground up specifically for VR, created by and for board game enthusiasts. As **the only platform natively built for VR**, All On Board! fully exploits the capabilities of virtual reality to deliver an **unmatched board gaming experience**. This includes **predictive selection** and positioning of board elements while enjoying **realistic physical interactions** close to real life. A unique platform that is **constantly evolving**, both functionally and in its game catalog, packed with **beloved franchises** among board game enthusiasts.\n\nExperience the joy of discovering new games, just like browsing the latest releases at your favorite store: All On Board! brings you shared moments of discussion, laughter, and nostalgia reminiscent of past adventures and unforgettable games.\n\n# Features:\n- **Only one player is required to purchase game titles**: If you own a game, you can invite your friends to play for free, just like in real life\n- Experience interactions that are **intuitive and naturally immersive**\n- **Top-tier games meticulously adapted for VR**, ensuring exceptional gameplay and smooth interactions\n- Quickly learn the rules with **in-game tutorials and contextual help** that provides more information about any component\n- **Tailored gameplay for 1 to multiple players,** including solo and co-op modes. You can even tackle cooperative games on your own!\n- **Cross-platform support**\n- Play in your preferred language, with **ongoing additions to our language support**", "short_description": "Designed from the ground up for VR, All On Board! offers seamless board game experiences. Join this ever-evolving platform and connect with fellow board game enthusiasts! Choose your avatar and enjoy playing solo or with friends, diving into some of the most popular board game franchises."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://thegamekitchen.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "The Game Kitchen", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://thegamekitchen.com/all-on-board-vr/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "es"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER", "SINGLE_USER", "CO_OP"], "id": "8445333772199824"}, "review_messages": ["", "", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75630196_883361956748345_3217241762219801412_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Nn-dH8xJbSgQ7kNvgER4FTr&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDXxSaYzK-WD7DWE81fAECp44iyFBY0qeqfXASznDseFw&oe=671382EB"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "All On Board! - Demo", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "2743326035925534"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Social", "id": "1573854509480616"}, {"topic_name": "Casual", "id": "394813081514456"}, {"topic_name": "Simulation", "id": "331529188132278"}], "release_date": 1728895980, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "8354509374615598", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "8354509344615601", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "3411048245859046"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1726140801497135", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "All On Board! - Demo", "keywords": ["tabletop", "indie", "multiplayer", "online", "board"], "long_description": "All On Board! es una plataforma de juegos de mesa creada desde cero para la realidad virtual, hecha por y para los amantes de los juegos de mesa. Como **la \u00fanica plataforma nativa para VR**, All On Board! aprovecha al m\u00e1ximo las capacidades de la realidad virtual para ofrecer una **experiencia inigualable**. Esto incluye la **selecci\u00f3n predictiva** y el posicionamiento de los elementos del tablero, con **interacciones f\u00edsicas realistas** y cercanas a la vida real. Es **una plataforma que evoluciona constantemente**, tanto en su funcionalidad como en su cat\u00e1logo de juegos, con **franquicias muy queridas** por los fans de los juegos de mesa.\n\nDescubre nuevos juegos como si estuvieras explorando las \u00faltimas novedades de tu tienda favorita. All On Board! te ofrece momentos compartidos de debate, risas y nostalgia, recordando partidas y aventuras inolvidables.\n\n# Caracter\u00edsticas:\n\n- **Solo un jugador necesita comprar el juego**: si lo tienes, invita a tus amigos a jugar gratis, \u00a1igual que en la vida real!\n- **Interacciones intuitivas e inmersivas**.\n- **Los mejores juegos adaptados para VR**, asegurando jugabilidad y fluidez excepcionales.\n- Aprende r\u00e1pido con **tutoriales integrados y ayuda contextual**.\n- **Juegos para 1 o varios jugadores**, con modos en solitario y cooperativo. \u00a1Incluso puedes jugar juegos cooperativos por tu cuenta!\n- **Compatibilidad entre plataformas**.\n- Juega en tu idioma preferido, con **soporte de idiomas en constante expansi\u00f3n**.", "short_description": "Dise\u00f1ado desde cero para la realidad virtual, All On Board! te ofrece experiencias de juegos de mesa sin igual. \u00danete a esta plataforma en constante evoluci\u00f3n y conecta con otros entusiastas de los juegos de mesa. Elige tu avatar y disfruta jugando solo o con amigos, sumergi\u00e9ndote en algunas de las franquicias de juegos de mesa m\u00e1s populares."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Portrait.png", "id": "1704444607063428", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974853_1704444610396761_8129462956027802645_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5XDcyq96-f8Q7kNvgHhEEKJ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDdaNTpWEyBJL7JKxE5ufyuXf6m3gDwhOCb3aq0O0Ce5g&oe=6713A2A1"}, {"f